data: {"p":"response/fragments/-1/results","v":[{"url":"https://sn.ifeng.com/c/8rkgWf9MtaO","title":"2026世界杯前瞻：365体育分析三强鼎立，北美亚洲新篇章——当足球盛宴首次跨越三国，48支劲旅将如何重绘世界足坛版图？","snippet":"二、 夺冠热门巡礼：新旧势力的巅峰对决 ... 1. 法国队：姆巴佩时代的开启 ... 2. 阿根廷队：梅西的谢幕与传承 ... 三、 东道主表现：美加墨的足球野望","cite_index":1,"published_at":1774281600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/ifeng.com","site_name":"凤凰网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/SportsArchive/2026-FIFA-World-Cup-Spain-lead-ESPN-s-rankings-as-favorites-2027229","title":"2026 FIFA World Cup: Spain lead ESPN's rankings as favorites","snippet":"contenders. Topping the list is Spain, a nation that has won the World Cup once, in 2010. Spain’s recent resurgence, highlighted by strong performances in international competitions, signals a return to elite status. ... two-time world champions (1998, 2018)...","cite_index":2,"published_at":1774281600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/ghanaweb.com","site_name":"GhanaWeb","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://voice.hupu.com/bbs/635871471","title":"英媒评-国际足球-国际足球资讯-虎扑社区","snippet":"前日本国脚本田圭佑坚称他们有潜力加冕大力神杯，这目前来看或许有点牵强，但他们肯定是一支实力强劲的球队，在各位置上都拥有优秀球员。 《足球部落》：美加墨世界杯夺冠热门TOP10 1 西班牙 2 阿根廷 3 英格兰 4 法国 5 葡萄牙 6 巴西 7 挪威 8 摩洛哥","cite_index":3,"published_at":1763654400.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/hupu.com","site_name":"虎扑","query_indexes":[0,2]},{"url":"https://www.si.com/soccer/world-cup-2026-power-rankings-spain-argentina-favorites-norway-dark-horses","title":"World Cup 2026 Power Rankings: Spain & Argentina Favorites, Norway the Dark Horses","snippet":"Here, Sports Illustrated unveils its 2026 World Cup Power Rankings, breaking down the 20 leading contenders based on qualifying form, momentum, squad strength and everything else in between. ## 20. Uruguay ... 18. Switzerland ... 16. Belgium","cite_index":4,"published_at":1773936000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/si.com","site_name":"Sports Illustrated","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"http://m.pdvolunteer.org.cn/news/zuqiu/19264.html","title":"超级计算机预测2026年冠军：阿森纳领跑，西班牙成世界杯头号热门","snippet":"在英格兰赛场，阿森纳被Opta视为最大夺冠热门。模型显示，“枪手”赢得2025/26赛季英超冠军的概率高达78.98%，远超曼城（16.69%）。","cite_index":5,"published_at":1767369600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/pdvolunteer.org.cn","site_name":"pdvolunteer.org.cn","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.foxsports.com/stories/soccer/2026-world-cup-power-rankings-why-colombia-belongs-top-5","title":"2026 World Cup Power Rankings: Why Colombia Belongs In the Top 5","snippet":"11: #10 United States previously unranked FIFA Rank: 15 ... It’s not crazy to put USA here in the top-10. In the FIFA Rankings, the U.S. is at 15th, but again, this isn’t just a World Cup...","cite_index":6,"published_at":1772640000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/foxsports.com","site_name":"FOX Sports","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://www.thedailystar.net/sports/football/news/2026-fifa-world-cup-how-favourites-stack-4050361","title":"2026 FIFA World Cup: How the favourites stack up","snippet":"Ahead of Friday's 2026 World Cup draw, here we take a look at the leading contenders at the first-ever 48-team finals to take place across North America next June and July (current world ranking in brackets): ## Spain (1)","cite_index":7,"published_at":1764777600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/thedailystar.net","site_name":"The Daily Star","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://m.qtx.com/worldcup/276955.html","title":"今年世界杯冠亚季军预测 西班牙成最大热门","snippet":"2026年美加墨世界杯的冠亚季军争夺，大概率仍将集中在欧洲传统豪强与少数南美劲旅之间，西班牙、法国、英格兰三支球队成为冠亚季军的热门人选，这一预测也贴合当前足坛的实力格局与主流夺冠赔率走向，各支球队的竞争优势与潜在短板，也决定了其在世界杯赛场的大概率走势。","cite_index":8,"published_at":1771430400.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/qtx.com","site_name":"球天下","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://mauth.cbssports.com/soccer/news/2026-world-cup-power-rankings-usmnt-argentina-spain-brazil-mexico/","title":"2026 World Cup Power Rankings: USMNT close to top 10; Lionel Messi's Argentina not No. 1","snippet":"2026 World Cup Power Rankings: USMNT close to top 10; Lionel Messi's Argentina not No. 1 ## The 2026 World Cup will take place next year in the United States, Mexico and Canada","cite_index":9,"published_at":1763481600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/cbssports.com","site_name":"CBS Sports","query_indexes":[2]}]}

